<sect1 id="dir_014d03f1fa745a752e3155249a7cef2e_1autotoc_md191">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::gamestate</title><para>Game state management system for the helios engine.</para>
<para>This module provides a rule-based state machine for managing game states (e.g., Title, Running, Paused) with transitions, listeners, and command-driven state changes.</para>
</sect1>
