<sect1 id="dir_014d03f1fa745a752e3155249a7cef2e_1autotoc_md193">
<title>Architecture</title><para>1. <bold>GameStateManager</bold> holds the transition rules and processes state commands 2. <bold>GameStateCommand</bold> encapsulates a transition request 3. <bold>GameStateTransitionRule</bold> defines valid from -&gt; to transitions with optional guards 4. <bold>GameStateTransitionListener</bold> implementations react to state changes</para>
</sect1>
